column2: Welcome to PremiumExtract! This is a risk-controlled strategy based on swing trading, primarily using Put Credit Spreads, Call Credit Spreads, and Iron Condors to capture premium over time.
The strategy uses defined-risk spreads, which limits potential downsides compared to selling naked options. These spreads are beginner-friendly and easy to master.
Below is the historical performance since August 2023, showing strong results.
For now, trade alerts are free, but in the future, I plan to introduce a small monthly fee (just a cup of coffee!). Your support will help me keep improving and providing value to the community.

More trades will be placed moving forward. Past performance doesnâ€™t guarantee future results, and risk management is essential. This strategy has performed well over the past months, but it's important to understand there are no guarantees.
Please apply proper risk management and remember that these are trade ideas.
